TITLE : SPACE-ACE (Shooting game)

PLAYING INSTRUCTION:
KEY_UP = To move the tank up
KEY_DOWN = To move the tank down
SPACE BAR = To shoot bullet 

AIM AND SCORING:
The alien ship moves up and down and moves towards the tank after each lap.
Shoot the alien and earn 20 points for each hit to the mini ship.
Every shot which does not hit the mini ship results in deduction of a point.
Stay away from the bombs fired by the alien ship and shoot them at the same time to earn +5 points.


UPCOMING FEATURES:
1)Highscore Functionality
2)Different difficulty levels

